{"tid":335828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨涂謹申：將部分土地交給內地可以避免牴觸基本法！","createTime":"2017-07-26T02:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T09:40:17.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"630b6017dc05e57c51639d07466b079861686dfe","tid":335828,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:03:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/855088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F855088%2F&d=ZZgZ4TDTz8rabxIAk%2BwzNgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a0202903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F855088%2F&h=c1309246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/855088/</a><br />\n高鐵預料於明年第三季通車，近日接連有高鐵西九龍總站不同階段的設計圖則曝光，顯示政府已預留地方作「一地兩檢」，但法律問題遲遲未能解決。港澳辦主任王光亞昨在北京表示，兩地政府本月中旬會就高鐵「一地兩檢」問題進行協商，形容「應該說是有進展」。 <br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員胡漢清日前則建議以「割地」模式，將部分高鐵總站內的地方、以至高鐵沿線列車劃為內地管轄區。 <br />\n立法會保安事務委員會副主席涂謹申亦指，香港高鐵範圍內設內地管轄區「技術上好多年前都提過」，但困難是內地人員不能在港執法，建議可將車站部分土地交給內地政府，縮少香港領土範圍，可以避免牴觸《基本法》，但認為涉及港人信心問題，因市民會擔心先例一開，香港面積會不斷減少。"},{"pid":"60a2a74d874c3dda76fc4c61f56104dcf049eb63","tid":335828,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4f830057c99b095790008d302c6ad17aa826c6","tid":335828,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:05:31.000Z","msg":"預左架啦"},{"pid":"efb8256af9d1fe2b01e530c0374dad2a75c9458b","tid":335828,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:18:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/855088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F855088%2F&d=ZZgZ4TDTz8rabxIAk%2BwzNgEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=a0202903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F855088%2F&h=c1309246\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/855088/</a><br />\n高鐵預料於明年第三季通車，近日接連有高鐵西九龍總站不同階段的設計圖則曝光，顯示政府已預留地方作「一地兩檢」，但法律問題遲遲未能解決。港澳辦主任王光亞昨在北京表示，兩地政府本月中旬會就高鐵「一地兩檢」問題進行協商，形容「應該說是有進展」。 <br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員胡漢清日前則建議以「割地」模式，將部分高鐵總站內的地方、以至高鐵沿線列車劃為內地管轄區。 <br />\n立法會保安事務委員會副主席涂謹申亦指，香港高鐵範圍內設內地管轄區「技術上好多年前都提過」，但困難是內地人員不能在港執法，建議可將車站部分土地交給內地政府，縮少香港領土範圍，可以避免牴觸《基本法》，但認為涉及港人信心問題，因市民會擔心先例一開，香港面積會不斷減少。</blockquote><br />\n涂謹申<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b25d7247850a15f10dbf79258224da23252358b","tid":335828,"uid":34831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T02:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a0df43d54290484d616b44d06765620b8989ba","tid":335828,"uid":12185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T03:03:42.000Z","msg":"取消一國兩制可辦免抵觸基本上"},{"pid":"324d1b2be4ef1d97edeb9e289e64bf634de99ebe","tid":335828,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"天水圍啦"},{"pid":"01f713f3701cb27836bff9c2bc09243387f905f2","tid":335828,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-26T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"實施一地兩檢不違基本法　涂謹申：港可撥部西九站份土地予內地 <br />\n<br />\n撰文：\t黎梓緯 <br />\n<br />\n發佈日期：2017-03-08 09:39 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家又出黎扮野話反對到底<br />\n<br />\n點解民主黨仆街到咁仲有人信"},{"pid":"187ecca1151e025fcdd605e26c29e97f6d379fc6","tid":335828,"uid":79563,"like":0,"disl